item.description:
Come join me for a night of disc tossing and excersize as we walk the trails along the course. You don't have to be good at throwing a frisbee but come along and give it a try and have some fun. We will meet at the Hillside General store and get our discs then head to the park across the street to the park..We can stop for an ice cream after if s=we finish before the store closes too. Remember to bring water, good shoes and BUG SPRAY.

here's a link to the get some more info on the course
